<section class="space-y-4">
  <p>
    Агент, добро пожаловать в <span class="text-cyan-300 font-semibold">AgentArchive</span> — центральный архив оперативного отдела.
    После атаки NULL система забыла, какие агенты существуют, какими навыками они владеют и на какие задания назначены.
  </p>

  <div class="rounded-xl border border-cyan-900/70 bg-cyan-950/20 p-4">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-500 mb-3">Предметная область</div>
    <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-gray-200 marker:text-cyan-400">
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Agents</span> — оперативные агенты системы</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Skills</span> — навыки агентов</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Missions</span> — задания, закреплённые за агентами</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-xl border border-cyan-900/70 bg-cyan-950/20 p-4 mt-2">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-500 mb-4">Целевая схема БД</div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-xs font-mono">

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-cyan-800/60 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-cyan-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 text-cyan-300 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide">agents</div>
        <table class="w-full">
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800/60">
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/50"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-400">id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-cyan-600 text-[10px]">PK</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">codename</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-yellow-300">VARCHAR</span> <span class="text-red-400/70 text-[10px]">UQ</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">level</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">1..10</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">active</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-violet-400">BOOLEAN</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">created_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">updated_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-cyan-800/60 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-cyan-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 text-cyan-300 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide">missions</div>
        <table class="w-full">
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800/60">
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/50"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-400">id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-cyan-600 text-[10px]">PK</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">agent_id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-yellow-500/70 text-[10px]">FK → agents</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">title</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-yellow-300">VARCHAR</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">status</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-yellow-300">VARCHAR</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">enum</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">created_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">updated_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-cyan-800/60 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-cyan-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 text-cyan-300 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide">agent_skills</div>
        <table class="w-full">
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800/60">
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/50"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-400">id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-cyan-600 text-[10px]">PK</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">agent_id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-yellow-500/70 text-[10px]">FK → agents</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">skill_id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-yellow-500/70 text-[10px]">FK → skills</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">created_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">updated_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="px-3 py-1 text-[10px] text-red-400/70 border-t border-gray-800/60">UQ: [agent_id, skill_id]</div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-cyan-800/60 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-cyan-900/50 px-3 py-1.5 text-cyan-300 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide">skills</div>
        <table class="w-full">
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800/60">
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/50"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-400">id</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-amber-400">INTEGER</span> <span class="text-cyan-600 text-[10px]">PK</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">name</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-yellow-300">VARCHAR</span> <span class="text-red-400/70 text-[10px]">UQ</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-3 py-1 text-white">category</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-yellow-300">VARCHAR</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">null</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">created_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-900/30"><td class="px-3 py-1 text-gray-500">updated_at</td><td class="px-3 py-1 text-right"><span class="text-teal-400/70">TIMESTAMP</span></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-[11px] text-gray-500">
      <span>agents <span class="text-cyan-600">1</span> → <span class="text-cyan-600">N</span> missions</span>
      <span>agents <span class="text-cyan-600">1</span> → <span class="text-cyan-600">N</span> agent_skills</span>
      <span>skills <span class="text-cyan-600">1</span> → <span class="text-cyan-600">N</span> agent_skills</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-500 mb-3">Этапы восстановления</div>
    <ol class="list-decimal space-y-3 pl-5 marker:text-cyan-400">
      <li>
        Создай модель <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">Agent</code> и миграцию с полями
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">codename:string</code>,
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">level:integer</code>,
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">active:boolean</code>.
      </li>
      <li>
        Добавь модель <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">Skill</code> с полями
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">name:string</code> и
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">category:string</code>.
      </li>
      <li>
        Добавь модели <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">Mission</code> и
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">AgentSkill</code>.
      </li>
      <li>
        Настрой ассоциации:
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 marker:text-cyan-400 text-gray-300">
          <li>у агента много заданий, одна задание всегда выполняет один агент;</li>
          <li>у агента может быть много навыков;</li>
          <li>один навык может принадлежать многим агентам.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Добавь валидации для обязательных полей, уникальности и статусов миссии.
        Кодовые имена агентов должны быть уникальными, уровень должен быть числом от 1 до 10,
        а статус миссии может быть только "assigned", "in_progress", или "completed".
      </li>
      <li>
        Защити схему ограничениями БД: внешние ключи, уникальные индексы и составной индекс на
        <code class="rounded bg-gray-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-green-300">[agent_id, skill_id]</code>.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
